      "width": 440.2116553132267,
      "height": 231.44934324782653,
      "text": "Use **Pei De Shi**.\n\n* It keeps the rhythm of **Peter Scriol** without turning into a fake accent joke.\n* **Pei / De / Shi** all look plausible in pinyin to English speakers.\n* A cleaner full-name version is **Shi Peide**, which reads more like an actual Chinese name format.",
